sql_explorer:rag_example_queries.sql_query: select location_code , COUNT(DISTINCT pick_task_code) AS activePickOrders FROM `gold_pick` where location_code != '' and  date(event_timestamp_utc) >= date_trunc(date_sub(current_date(), INTERVAL 6 month), month) and  date(event_timestamp_utc) < date_trunc(current_date(), month) group by location_code order by COUNT(DISTINCT pick_task_code) desc limit 3;
